name: Star Wars
description: In the surreal landscapes of the Star Wars desert in Tunisia, our venue offers a cinematic experience for your events. With vast golden dunes stretching as far as the eye can see, this iconic location provides a unique and awe-inspiring backdrop. Immerse your guests in the magic of this legendary setting, where the allure of the desert meets the mystique of intergalactic adventures. Elevate your events with a touch of cinematic history at our Star Wars desert venue in Tunisia

name: Pinehomestay
description: Nestled in serene surroundings beneath a pine tree, our cabin offers tranquility with the sea, forest, and mountains as a picturesque backdrop. Just an hour from the capital, this space invites you to escape into nature. Enjoy a private retreat with a double bed, bathroom, terrace, and a kitchen with a bar. Join us for an unforgettable event and experience in this haven of peace.
